{"tid":1895271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實依家係唔係看圖說故事嘅年代？","createTime":"2020-02-24T12:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T12:33:05.000Z","uid":80164,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"475be7fb9f3c088fb398a089efd5d50c780770d8","tid":1895271,"uid":80164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:23:59.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n突然見到有條日本仔係推特上面話<br />\n「突然倒下嘅人急増<br />\n香港荃灣廣場<br />\n攤咗係地上好似痙攣咁款。<br />\n佢係因為武漢肺炎入咗肺所以係度慘叫」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s2U90fO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs2U90fO.png&h=99c080ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我係荃灣住咗咁撚耐就無見過有個地方係大大隻字寫住</span> <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">收费</span></span> 嘅<br />\n無睇錯嘅話呢條應該係武漢肺炎爆發之前中國啲咩漫展個陣嘅片嚟<br />\n咁同班藍屍有咩分別，望住張圖／條片鐘意作咩就作咩<br />\n<br />\n而最可怕嘅係呢個推嘅轉推數同比心數嘅增長速度係非常之快，一個鐘已經有500個以上轉推<br />\n即使你話呢單野唔係真，都會有一堆人走埋嚟話返你<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「玩梗啫，你唔係唔識呀？咁認真做咩？」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SfYOwrL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSfYOwrL.png&h=8dcf78a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dyXPfT8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdyXPfT8.png&h=679517cb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">拎武漢肺炎嚟玩，你地無撚野呀？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n覺得呢種弱智日本仔都應該死清光<br />\n求其拎條片就話係香港乜乜染染，大家可唔可以幫手一齊report佢個AC同個post呀？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAC: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Dieselkarui\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDieselkarui&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwbvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=59b4e2ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Dieselkarui</a><br />\nPost: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Dieselkarui/status/1231806147281051651\" data-s